Producer and Consumer examples in Apache Kafka 1.0.0, build in Hadoop ecosystem 2.6.7. Example done in JAVA, can be replicated to Scala as
well.

Schema serialization and de-serialization done using Apache Avro 1.8.2.

The producer and consumer folder have identical files.
1. Producer/Consumers.java
2. .sbt file for MAven repository build
3. .avsc file for AVRO schema
